data.text:
Royal response from Their Royal Highnesses Prince Laurent and Princess Claire of Belgium on the occasion of their wedding. Prince Laurent is the second son and youngest child of Their Majesties King Albert II and Queen Paola of Belgium and the younger brother of His Majesty The King of The Belgians. They were married on 12th April 2003 at the Cathedral of Saints Michael and Gudula. They have three children together, a daughter Prince Louise born 2004 and twin sons Prince Nicolas and Prince Aymeric born 2005.
